title: 3br house on quiet block, 5 min to DT
posting_body: ['3 BR LR DR fenced yard, off street parking, near bus line, close to every thing, 5 minuets to DT.', 'rent is $ 1,600.00 plus all utilities.', 'Available now for showing.', 'please text', 'show contact info', 'or email full names and date of birth of all adults planing to live in the unit for pre-screening', 'Application Fee: $35 per adult', 'The $35 application fee per adult will be used to conduct a background check that encompasses the following four areas:', '(1) Criminal history', '(2) Employment/Wage verification', '(3) Prior rental history', 'Requirements:', 'Clean criminal record per city guideline .', 'Good standing rental history, no evictions and/or unlawful detainers for the past 3 years.', 'Verifiable monthly income, 2.5 times the rent amount.', 'In order to secure the rental property the approved applicant is required to place a deposit', 'All approved tenants are required to sign up for Service Plus with Centerpoint Energy or HomeSmart with Xcel Energy upon approval']
